collection: The Last of Beta BM Collection
description: Audi revealed a limited edition of the RS e-tron GT with the same wild scheme on the 2020 prototype vehicle. "project_513/2" stands for the internal development code of this car which breaks down to cars segment, generation and body style (with a system Audi created i guess). Costs around $180k which is around $40k more than the normal RS e-tron GT. It is limited to only 75 units and exclusive to US market.
